OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FTwo women have died and 16 people have
OL,8,Fbeen injured trying to cross the
OL,9,FEnglish Channel in a small boat,
OL,10,FFrench authorities have said.
OL,12,FThe vessel, which was carrying 82
OL,13,Fpeople, set out overnight from
OL,14,FHardelot beach, close to the port of
OL,15,FBoulogne-sur-Mer on the west coast of
OL,16,FFrance, but its engine failed and it
OL,17,Fbegan to drift, said the secretary-
OL,18,Fgeneral of the Pas-de-Calais
OL,19,Fprefecture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
