FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FA French maritime gendarmerie boat was
OL,8,Fable to rescue 17 people, and brought
OL,9,Fthem to Boulogne-sur-Mer, while the
OL,10,Fmakeshift vessel ran aground with 65
OL,11,Fothers still on board, Christophe Marx
OL,12,Ftold a press briefing.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FTwo women were found dead inside the
OL,20,Fboat, most likely from suffocation,
OL,21,FMarx said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FHe said the women are thought to have
OL,8,Fbeen "crushed or asphyxiated", which
OL,9,Fcan happen when there are "too many
OL,10,Fpeople packed in" on a vessel.
OL,12,FThree others were injured with serious
OL,13,Fburns caused by fuel at the bottom of
OL,14,Fthe boat.
OL,16,FThe women were believed to be in their
OL,17,F20s and to have come from Sudan,
OL,18,Faccording to Marx, although some
OL,19,Freports have suggested one of them was
OL,20,Fa teenager.
OL,26,@pD@FOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FAn investigation is underway, Marx
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FIt is the third deadly incident
OL,11,Finvolving migrants trying make the
OL,12,Fperilous crossing to the UK in just
OL,13,Fover a month.
OL,15,FLast month, two men and two women died
OL,16,Fas they were trying to board an
OL,17,Finflatable boat off the coast of
OL,18,Fnorthern France, leading to British
OL,19,Fauthorities arresting a man from Sudan
OL,20,Fon suspicion of endangering life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FThe week before, two other people died
OL,8,Fin similar circumstances off the coast
OL,9,Fnorth of Calais.
OL,11,FThe UK and French governments signed a
OL,12,Fnew multimillion-euro deal last month
OL,13,Faimed at reducing the number of
OL,14,Fmigrants crossing the English Channel,
OL,15,Fwith increased police patrols and
OL,16,Fenhanced surveillance in northern
OL,17,FFrance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
