PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777842664
OL,3,CTwo women die and 16 injured in
OL,4,Cattempt to cross English Channel by
OL,5,Cboat
OL,7,FSo far this year, more than 6,000
OL,8,Fmigrants have reached the UK after
OL,9,Fcrossing the channel, down 36% from
OL,10,Fthe same period last year, a drop that
OL,11,Fmay partly reflect more unsettled
OL,12,Fweather.
OL,14,FBefore Sunday's deaths, migrant aid
OL,15,Fgroup Utopia 56 said that at least 172
OL,16,Fpeople have died at the French-UK
OL,17,Fborder over the past three years,
OL,18,Fincluding 123 at sea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
